      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still retains its original factory aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. The engine bay is detailed to perfection, showing no signs of fluid seepage or wear. This sale includes both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-grade example of automotive excellence.",
